  "2026-07-06T13:13:37.948Z",maintainer-agent,"Audit #10 2026-07-06 scope addition: GH-455 (health auto-selects uninstalled Ollama embedding model) is fixed — pm-aems closed via PR #464, shipped in release 2026.7.6 (npm verified). The GitHub issue is still open; close it with the fix reference in the same triage pass as GH-436/GH-440."
close_reason: completed
body: "## Context\n2026-07-06 audit #7 verified two open dogfood GH issues against pm 2026.7.5 in this workspace and both report already-shipped features:\n- GH-436 \"Port the MCP-only pm next and pm focus tools to the CLI\" — `pm next` (PR#357, src/core/item/actionability.ts) and `pm focus` (PR#257) are first-class CLI commands and work live.\n- GH-440 \"Add --fields projection to pm context\" — `pm context --fields id,title` works live (shipped PR#297).\n\n## Action\nClose both GH issues with a comment citing the shipping PRs and the verified version (2026.7.5); if the reporter hit an older global install, note the upgrade path. No code change needed unless re-verification finds an edge (e.g. focus-as-default-parent parity claimed by GH-436 — spot-check `pm create` honors focused item as default parent before closing).\n\n## Definition of done\nGH-436 + GH-440 closed with evidence comments; focus->default-parent parity spot-checked; this chore closed with resolution fields."
